{"tid":2106844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初選過後,其實我地應該諗下...","createTime":"2020-07-13T13:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T15:32:38.000Z","uid":69110,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed211d8ed5d0c91df0cc2d85c2e20a304bb311ea","tid":2106844,"uid":69110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"初選過後,其實我地應該諗下無投票嗰百幾萬黃絲會投邊個<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次初選,本土派同後生仔都有好多票,泛民嗰堆都得好少票咁,但主因都係真係有好多廿幾三十嘅出黎投票(當然都有唔少阿叔阿嬸老人家嘅)<br />\n<br />\n我地反而應該諗下無出黎投票嗰百幾萬淺黃/中產九月會投咩票<br />\n假設個選區得番2個泛民同4個後生/本土出黎選,佢地9成9都係投番出名嗰d (eg. gphone,岑子杰) 或者傳統泛民<br />\n到時好似新西嗰三個本土/坦克,仲係咪夠票入都好有疑問<br />\n<br />\n或者我地真係要好似保皇狗咁做好d配票,幾個後生仔一組咁去投票,先唔會出現贏票輸議席嘅情況"},{"pid":"43af3d7589a3071fa1abf59ce4362cb30dfe4182","tid":2106844,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"呢加少左界票<br />\n有得同民賤聯鬥"},{"pid":"76632482875e6c908cee1e09174bc2b0a8cbc8c3","tid":2106844,"uid":69110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac6de54e4590b816b4979f2527ca412cdb8d862d","tid":2106844,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67c9bbe9117b82838f3edcacad0ff9e6bb886792","tid":2106844,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">一句講哂，唔跟初選既全部都唔係同路人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0355ffb99fb9cad8f581ac28b60166965956b6","tid":2106844,"uid":69110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:06:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff7606edcff00c9fc6a86e74fc57f68c0f840a25","tid":2106844,"uid":96091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"所以要配票"},{"pid":"cc3ba7c242fd2e2bd910f606e60292116d0362e9","tid":2106844,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco